<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Worker_cooperative&amp;action=edit&amp;section=22" title="Edit section: External links">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">External links</span></h2>
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" class="multicol" style="background:transparent; width:100%;">
<tr>
